I had some more skillz this time around and I could reuse the theme I had already built.</p>
<p>Since most of the Bitesized cover art is greyscale, I went with a simple greyscale look.</p>
<p>Bitesized is a DIY band. I tried conveying this by using a handwritten font in the headers and by incorporating custom handwritten letters in the logo.</p>
<p>Website features include:</p>
<ul>
<li>a rectangle animation when a user hovers over links</li>
<li>social media icons</li>
<li>a scaling animation when a user hovers over social media icons</li>
</ul>
<p>One of my favourite parts is how the simplified logo in the favicon turned out.</p>







    
        
    

    






