        alt=""
        loading="lazy">
</a>

<p>I found the combination of bright greens in younger leaves, the deep dark greens in mature ones, and the yellowish-brown colour of an occasional dead leaf interesting. Since I had three canvases, I tried painting something resembling three stages of a plant&rsquo;s life.</p>
<p>Getting the colours right took some trial and error.</p>







    

    

    

    

    
        
    

    






<a href="https://tlocrt.com/visual/paintings/life_of_a_plant/images/life_of_a_plant_paint_mixing.jpg">
